      "solution": "#include <iostream>\n#include <cmath>\nusing namespace std;\n\nint main()\n{\n    int a;\n    cin >> a; cin.ignore();\n\n    bool ok = false;\n    int b=1;\n    while (!ok) {\n        int s=a*a+b*b, r = floor(sqrt(s)+0.5);\n        if (r*r==s) ok = true;\n        else ++b;\n    }\n    cout << b << endl;\n}\n",
